// These prevent SyncThing from trying to sync data that's locked, constantly
// changing, going to be thrown out, unimportant, etc.
// Lots of conflicts/issues disappeared using these ignores, but do check to
// prevent major disappointment!
// *.log and *cache* are in there, just so you know.. but firefox' startupCache
// and offlineCache will be synced.
// Decided to stop categorizing these. Sorting them Lexicographically from now
// on. Ignores are case sensitive.

